{"tid":2255344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府指英政府BNO安排嚴重干預特區事務　","createTime":"2020-10-23T12:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T15:20:47.000Z","uid":10757,"like":4,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"45e75c20f83dda1ecf978f1615f072121f7a2ae4","tid":2255344,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:51:38.000Z","msg":"英國政府明年1月31日起，接受合資格申請BNO港人，申請簽證到當地工作或留學，以回應北京實施港區國安法。政府發言人回覆表示，英國政府藉為持有英國國民(海外)護照或合資格持有者，提供在英居留和入籍路徑，以干預香港特區事務，特區政府對此表示不滿及反對。發言人表示，英國政府以《港區國安法》為藉口所採取的措施，純屬政治操作，嚴重違背自身在與中國政府互換的英方備忘錄所作出的承諾，亦嚴重干預香港特區的事務，特區政府敦促英國政府停止干預香港特區事務，重回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n2020-10-23 20:48:59"},{"pid":"251ca64f14c885fffd3975eb8ac3808457dcb830","tid":2255344,"uid":46746,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:55:10.000Z","msg":"又干涉人地國家內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044e230c0957ad1d2711201855c3a0c54b6dda2a","tid":2255344,"uid":36152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"So?"},{"pid":"0f01e4d5a974e0c265995d1f0fd5f48221b7909b","tid":2255344,"uid":33028,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"唔反制?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94f4a49a232ff6085bd770e01f12f9312d4c034","tid":2255344,"uid":14449,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:56:30.000Z","msg":"好心就改下份稿啦"},{"pid":"d8c362c765c0fe739f0891f08b0b5385ae5ba460","tid":2255344,"uid":152476,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"英國政府處理英藉關你乜事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27346314d91434fb84ecabf45acaff4d8eaeb76d","tid":2255344,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"3d33c059cf5aaf2b2bdd305a01a49701fd9b804f","tid":2255344,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,